metadata.name: Metaverse Chess Club Member NFT #1
metadata.description: Welcome to THE official chess club of the metaverse. Our members include some of the finest, most tenured Grand Masters alive today and our community is constantly growing. Official members get free entry into a multitude of prestigious chess events each month including but not limited to exhibition tournaments/simuls with chess masters, access to never before seen chess lessons from the greats, and free entry to tournaments every month with ETH and NFT prizes. Be sure to join our Discord community at the following link! https://discord.gg/dSBcBB9Rzu
